data.title: 500 Freedom Struggle MCQ
data.meta_description: 500 Freedom Struggle MCQ - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This free ebook contains 500+ MCQs on the Indian freedom struggle for UPSC EPFO 2021 exams. The document lists 32 multiple choice questions about important figures, events, theories, and works related to India's independence movement. It provides the questions, answer options for each, and indicates the correct answer.
